title: Pneumatic Railroad Interlockings
name: Pneumatic Railroad Interlockings
description:
A Map by Sturmovik

This is a map of the surviving railroad and rail transit interlockings which utilize air powered switch machines like the US&amp;S A-5 and A-10.  While superior in operation the higher maintenance costs encourage railroads to replace the machines with electric models.  This map hopes to document the surviving instillations.
